title: Change 4 Change Giveback
itunes:title: Change 4 Change Giveback
description:
Times can be hard, especially during holiday season, so today on the show we had our "Change 4 Change" event, but instead of asking for money we decided to give back to some of our listeners who fell on hard times and make their holiday season a little less stress and happier.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
